285
00:18:19,160 --> 00:18:20,520
Cherry

286
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:27,280
Why did you put the damaged product with other showcase products?

287
00:18:27,600 --> 00:18:28,920
Well…

288
00:18:29,280 --> 00:18:31,360
Someone from the Design Department took the old one

289
00:18:31,640 --> 00:18:34,240
So I put this one here for the time being.

290
00:18:34,600 --> 00:18:37,680
I will find a new one to showcase here shortly

291
00:18:38,360 --> 00:18:39,440
Cherry,

292
00:18:40,360 --> 00:18:41,480
I have told you many times

293
00:18:41,720 --> 00:18:42,640
You should be more careful.

294
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:45,120
I’m sorry.

295
00:18:47,600 --> 00:18:49,640
You are new interns here, right?

296
00:18:50,320 --> 00:18:51,520
Yes.

297
00:18:52,080 --> 00:18:53,360
My name is Yong.

298
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:55,680
